==English==

===Noun===
{{en-noun|sg=[[ghetto]] [[fence]]}}

# A crudely constructed [[barrier]] intended to keep one group (usually against their will) separate from another.

# An intermediary in a territorial dispute among homeless individuals.  In use: "Hobo Jim is using that discarded folding chair as a ghetto fence to stop the Pigeon lady from taking his cardboard box."

